# GitHub Personal Access Token for bug reporting
# Setup instructions:
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens/new
# 2. Create a new Fine-grained personal access token
# 3. Grant permissions for: sudosar/quraniq-kids repository
# 4. Scopes needed: Contents (read/write), Issues (read/write)
# 5. Copy the token and paste into .env.local
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...your_token_here...
